---
import { FREEPHONE_NUMBER } from '../../../../../utils/constants';

interface Props {
	location: string;
	locationTel: string;
}

const { location, locationTel } = Astro.props;
---

<h2 class="h3">
	Do you have an enquiry about Soakaways and Septic Tanks and live in {location} or the surrounding area?
</h2>
<h3 class="h4 coloured-text">
	Call us now on {
		locationTel ? locationTel : `Freephone ${FREEPHONE_NUMBER} - 24 hour Emergency Helpline`
	}
</h3>

<p>
	Over a period of time soakaways can silt up and not work as effectively as they should. We may be
	able to remedy this problem by simply jetting the drain run to the soakaway. However, if the
	problem is not rectified and you require a replacement or new soakaway we can assist in
	determining the suitability or advice on type of soakaway.
</p>
<p>
	We are also able to give advice on all other types of sewage systems including Septic Tanks,
	Pumping Stations, and Sewage treatment plants.
</p>
<h3 class="h4">
	For specialist drainage installation reqirements in {location} call us today and discover why we are
	rated so highly by our customers.
</h3>
